Software updates should be run at minimum every 30 days. Run the following command to verify when software update was previously run:           $ sudo defaults read /Library/Preferences/com.apple.SoftwareUpdate | grep -e LastFullSuccessfulDate
. The response should be in the last 30 days (          Example
):           LastFullSuccessfulDate = "2020-07-30 12:45:25 +0000";
